metadata.name: Silken Wave
metadata.description:
Silken Wave captures the graceful, fluid movement I see in my floral subjects. Using my floral macro photograph as the seed image, the elements of nature and texture are blended, transforming the petals into a calming wave-like formation. 
Through the process of generating an AI image from my photograph, Silken Wave becomes an embodiment of natural beauty and abstract exploration and offers the viewer a visual meditation into nature's interconnectedness and artistic possibilities.


Ai piece created from my photograph 
by Renée Campbell 

5376px x 8064px JPG

About the artist:  
Macro photographer Renée Campbell finds meditation in photography, exploring the world around her through the petals. Her pieces have been displayed in both solo and group exhibitions in Sydney and New York, including Sotheby's. 
Renée's artistic repertoire has evolved to include AI-generated creations in addition to her macro photography, with a particular emphasis on floral subjects. Her work has also been displayed in NFT galleries in Los Angeles, New York, Athens, China and the UK, as well as several online group exhibitions.
